Package: BCIFeatR
Title: Feature Extraction Toolkit for Brain-Computer Interfaces
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R:
    person("Yiming", "Shen", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "yiming.shen001@umb.edu")
Description: A comprehensive feature extraction library for EEG-based
    brain-computer interfaces. Implements Common Spatial Patterns (CSP,
    FBCSP, FBCSSP), Riemannian geometry on SPD manifolds (tangent space,
    geodesic filtering, FGDA), Augmented Covariance Matrices (ACM),
    Avalanche Transition Matrices (ATM), log-variance features, and
    lightweight classifiers. Provides a unified train/test dispatcher
    with preprocessing, input validation, and metadata tracking.
